    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in style with this fantastic find! This car is in great shape and has been clearly well-cared for, offering a smooth and reliable driving experience you can count on. It shows some light, honest signs of use, but it remains a sharp-looking, high-quality vehicle that's ready for its next adventure. A wonderful opportunity for anyone seeking a dependable and attractive ride!",
