    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system for optimized torque across the powerband. Power is sent to the rear wheels via a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a variable M differential lock. Crucial preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a top-end service to ensure valvetrain longevity. The chassis remains composed with a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear suspension setup, offering the tactile feedback enthusiasts crave. A mechanically sound example with sharp throttle response and robust compression.",
