      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between performance and everyday utility. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, showing only the minor road wear expected from a car that has been enjoyed but respected. Inside, the cabin is a sanctuary of comfort; the leather seating remains supple with minimal signs of use, and all onboard technology\u2014from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014operates flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smooth and quiet, benefiting from a rigorous service schedule and proactive care. Recent maintenance includes a fresh set of high-performance tires and a comprehensive fluid flush. This car has been garage-kept and smoke-free, offering a reliable 'turn-key' experience for its next owner. Complete with a full set of service records and two sets of keys, it is ready for the open road.",
